Game will start with message "Guess the letter I am thinking of"
Computer will pick a letter at random from the array ["a","b","c"........."z"]
The user will select a letter 
if correct letter is guessed then "win" will count up
display " your guess is correct"
if incorrect letter is guessed 
        then "lose" will count up
        then "number of guesses" will count down
        then guesses you have made will start displaying the letters you typed.
if number of guesses =0 then display " game over- you lose"
if a key other than a letter in the alphabet is pressed display "Please pick a letter"